title: In-soo (Korean name)
text:
In-soo, also spelled In-su, is a Korean unisex given name. The meaning of the name differs based on the <a href="hanja">hanja</a> used to write each syllable. There are 29 hanja with the reading "<a href="In%20%28Korean%20name%29">in</a>" and 67 hanja with the reading "<a href="Soo%20%28Korean%20name%29">soo</a>" on the South Korean government's official list of hanja which may be used in given names.
